### 1. 查询所有服务人员 (GET)
GET http://localhost:8081/api/workers
Accept: application/json

### 2. 根据ID查询服务人员 (GET)
GET http://localhost:8081/api/workers/1
Accept: application/json

### 3. 根据工号查询服务人员 (GET)
GET http://localhost:8081/api/workers/no/SW001
Accept: application/json

### 4. 新增服务人员 (POST)
POST http://localhost:8081/api/workers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "workerNo": "SW001",
  "realName": "张三",
  "phone": "13800138001",
  "serviceLevel": "高级"
}

### 5. 更新服务人员 (PUT)
PUT http://localhost:8081/api/workers/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "workerNo": "SW001",
  "realName": "张三(已更新)",
  "phone": "13800138001",
  "serviceLevel": "特级"
}

### 6. 删除服务人员 (DELETE)
DELETE http://localhost:8081/api/workers/1
Accept: application/json
